{"tid":1996390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班傳媒係唔係拉得？","createTime":"2020-05-01T02:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T04:23:31.000Z","uid":196227,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8486252e6d3f057bb8d7dce9573b6626afe1b7f1","tid":1996390,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peULypX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeULypX.jpg&h=a8bb4d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996286\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996286</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係引起社會恐慌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本冇人出過黎話做咩<br />\n又話炸彈又話恐怖主義<br />\n佢係嚴重損害緊香港經濟<br />\n<br />\n5月1日只係個假日<br />\n<br />\n當一班人出黎話主張集會自由 - 拉<br />\n網上要求人罷買 - 拉<br />\n琼B share咗個post - 拉<br />\n黎生 - 拉<br />\n<br />\n依家佢地散播緊恐怖主義令我地唔敢消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n議員會唔會嘗試記低埋呢點<br />\n留備有用既1日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申今日只係想買好多野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同牙峯一齊撐黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91509feef77063ec2127ec6639fb5c2e9dc508c3","tid":1996390,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"撐🤚🏻☝🏻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3424adf4f7f6509d7914f8e87ae6a8ba0affabf5","tid":1996390,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"佢地有冇確切既來源證明係有人話放炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而有點解係發大黎講引起恐慌<br />\n而唔係交比班狗去調查<br />\n<br />\n如果依家猜測/鳩吹可以出份報紙<br />\n失實報道都算<br />\n仲要散播恐慌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88cdc71580af94b3b88dd7a5279e815acda900c","tid":1996390,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:01:42.000Z","msg":"如果最後冇炸彈爆到，係咪造謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac5c6152e55ef7b716160e926bb8f5ec0e5b7e1","tid":1996390,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996118\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996118</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打整合咗內容<br />\n<br />\n記者議員可以記一記低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知蘋果聽日頭條用唔用呢堆好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4ac5c6152e55ef7b716160e926bb8f5ec0e5b7e1","tid":1996390,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996118\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996118</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打整合咗內容<br />\n<br />\n記者議員可以記一記低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知蘋果聽日頭條用唔用呢堆好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}